{"tid":1506460,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[國際文宣] 點解Quora上面一面倒五毛抺黑示威者？我地d人呢？","createTime":"2019-08-25T20:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T02:12:32.000Z","uid":293282,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ba7a2f968be31f1a1f1b60f5321cd852c02dca84","tid":1506460,"uid":293282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T20:39:50.000Z","msg":"首先, in case手足有人唔知咩係Quora: Quora係一個鬼佬用既問答平台，你當係鬼佬版既Yahoo知識la。不用Quora既聲譽非常好，裏面答問題既人都必須有名有姓，好多答題者都係高級知識份子，就算你問d咩高級宇宙學問題你都可以搵到物理教授或者NASA員工答你。而且問問題同答問題既人受高好評既話Quora會出糧比佢，所以問答質素都有一定保證。<br />\n<br />\n不過，關於香港既問題，我岩岩一search，屌你老味，點解答問題既都係五毛抺黑示威者既？<br />\n<br />\n例如呢條，問究竟示威者定警察先撩者賤，最多人睇果個回應，8月15日至今已經有數以千計既view。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但，個，回，應，係，插，鳩，示，威，者，架！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.quora.com/Who-assaulted-first-the-protestors-or-the-Hong-Kong-police\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.quora.com%2FWho-assaulted-first-the-protestors-or-the-Hong-Kong-police&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxvTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=8d4cd2ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.quora.com/Who-assaulted-first-the-protestors-or-the-Hong-Kong-police</a><br />\n<br />\n其它既回應，都係一面倒插示威者。<br />\n<br />\n國際文宣組可唔可以都搵人係Quora做下野，係d熱門問題都貼下警暴片段/圖片做回應？起碼等d人click入去見到警察既惡行，而唔係俾五毛任意抺黑。<br />\n<br />\n要知道，Quora對外國既知識份子有一定影響力，係文宣既好渠道。知識份子對佢地國內又有影響力，甚至做佢地自己國內既國會遊說都係靠呢d人做起。<br />\n<br />\n唔該，幫幫手，搞搞Quora。<br />\n<br />\n我知道account要有名有姓，但佢唔需要身份證明文件驗證，所以唔用真名都可以開。<br />\n<br />\n文宣可以開一d account專問問題，再開另一d account專答問題。<br />\n<br />\n文宣組如果有人睇到，可唔可以麻煩share你地內部傾下, thx."},{"pid":"e4d9f0f278f4362c23b5ca9f4dd9622a6b358e64","tid":1506460,"uid":74591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T20:47:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eaf27362a7056f86f9faea591da09dcad6f2478a","tid":1506460,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T20:47:54.000Z","msg":"[突發]撐狗學生寫左封信比人民日報<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1506426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1506426</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n借推"},{"pid":"01ffb5291bf2d6b87886b4af814e078e3f3c58cb","tid":1506460,"uid":207259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T20:52:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b416b971c0045e03650c31f6c99931aa442587a","tid":1506460,"uid":50912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T20:54:10.000Z","msg":"推唔郁照推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4448b06f4785072c6c36cd8aa3797d69d7aea372","tid":1506460,"uid":63053,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T21:00:46.000Z","msg":"幾年前已經係咁<br />\n你呢個已經算少<br />\n有D抹黑我地既answer上千upvote 幾十萬views<br />\n完全淪陷"},{"pid":"cc309ea02f2523e6950a476bc75ca9a0069743a9","tid":1506460,"uid":63053,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T21:03:58.000Z","msg":"同埋好多loaded question<br />\n擺明自問自答<br />\n再用bot推上去<br />\n上面search示威既野 一面倒係佢地既問答"},{"pid":"7841c42b044be3a002aa52950008e5e4b3b350d8","tid":1506460,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T21:04:29.000Z","msg":"我幫你"},{"pid":"c9416de0d3bcb9bd17f225cb09313e74db715344","tid":1506460,"uid":158760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T21:05:17.000Z","msg":"Not a lot of Hong Kongers go to Quora.... won&rsquo;t be a big population <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf6ec8def89a5534d83d4f968ef172938687b33","tid":1506460,"uid":72800,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T21:10:14.000Z","msg":"出國留學既得利益者aka小粉紅<br />\n自我感覺良好文宣之地"},{"pid":"c4b0e455dcc413ff18dca189b3002be992c552e4","tid":1506460,"uid":176447,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T21:12:45.000Z","msg":"一早係淪陷區<br />\n五毛同自乾五集中地<br />\n擺嚮度由佢發臭好過俾返權威性俾呢個堆填區<br />\n會認真睇Quora嘅鬼佬都會摷其他website"},{"pid":"fc340d6890c8d74b22d76b3bbcf66508405b0f82","tid":1506460,"uid":293282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c9416de0d3bcb9bd17f225cb09313e74db715344","tid":1506460,"uid":158760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T21:05:17.000Z","msg":"Not a lot of Hong Kongers go to Quora.... won&rsquo;t be a big population <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T21:13:48.000Z","msg":"國際既support非常之重要，我地要打持久戰，遲d仲要向國際慕捐，叫國際商家sponsor，又要向各國既國會拖壓推政策幫香港，Quora影響國際知識份子甚深，唔可以唔守！"},{"pid":"6506d146c3ea81d1054e4c20912be8b763995669","tid":1506460,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T21:33:41.000Z","msg":"我一直都話前線唔岩<br />\n成班人話我五毛"},{"pid":"0e4be6f022dabdab47add67becb22899c00e03ba","tid":1506460,"uid":293282,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c4b0e455dcc413ff18dca189b3002be992c552e4","tid":1506460,"uid":176447,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T21:12:45.000Z","msg":"一早係淪陷區<br />\n五毛同自乾五集中地<br />\n擺嚮度由佢發臭好過俾返權威性俾呢個堆填區<br />\n會認真睇Quora嘅鬼佬都會摷其他website"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T21:39:23.000Z","msg":"我想反攻Quora. 我有諗過，可唔可以係其它地方進攻。<br />\n<br />\n例如，STEM型既鬼佬比社會科學型既鬼佬，少睇新聞。<br />\n<br />\nQuora文宣如果要做到簡單、低成本，可以只問問題，不回答。問STEM型既問題，但暗地裏潛藏香港。<br />\n<br />\n例如: 請問如果好似香港警察咁係地鐵站裏面放催淚彈，d山埃會留幾耐ga？<br />\n貼link: 由於每條問題可以貼一條link去說明問題，我建議貼多圖既新聞或者直接貼地鐵站催淚彈圖<br />\n<br />\n真係assign一d有權威既人去答，例如化學系教授，或者從事軍火工作既人。既可以draw attention，將來指控黑警又可以多d專業聲音去endorse。<br />\n<br />\n又例如可以問: <br />\n<br />\nSTEM類:<br />\n1. 請問按照被香港警察打穿眼既少女既傷勢，醫學上視力可以復原幾成呢？(貼link俾新聞，assign醫生作答)<br />\n2. 香港有監控鏡頭既智慧燈柱同新彊監視器係咪用同一款零件ga？(搵自己人作答，貼圖link)<br />\n<br />\n非STEM類:<br />\n1. 請問如果好似香港警察咁，打救護員，犯左咩國際法呢？ (搵自己人客觀作答)<br />\n2. 香港警察打記者有無真實證據ga？ (搵自己人客觀作答貼video link)<br />\n3. 香港警察叫市民蟑螂點解算係仇恨言論呢？ (搵自己人客觀作答，或者assign 法律專家/人權組織員工作答)"},{"pid":"8769c09d90d4c27e3a7f4d46fc0a83ea3fd2da89","tid":1506460,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T00:38:07.000Z","msg":"「圖」多個內地日文Twitter帳號惡意抹黑示威 並大量宣傳解放軍資訊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1506545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1506545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6f6447e5ca2538f03ec4231d920c9cd3ad8549ba","tid":1506460,"uid":283240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T00:50:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4da75fe2e95de00c11be5c1c50dd2a301b09fdd","tid":1506460,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:59:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有冇渠道文宣番去大陸?咪𨶙俾中共講晒</span>"},{"pid":"011d9231f32cd089cf723b993cfeec49619b09cb","tid":1506460,"uid":60208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:30:01.000Z","msg":"我都想玩quora，但一定要有一堆人做<br />\n唔夠Upvote你點打都無用"},{"pid":"f14b7f4e351c0b1d9b352d5ffa2e1d65162e1e45","tid":1506460,"uid":311004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:32:54.000Z","msg":"Quora本身就是五毛集中區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0066b24350a430ec2b860b8039b06016f5936b09","tid":1506460,"uid":60208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f14b7f4e351c0b1d9b352d5ffa2e1d65162e1e45","tid":1506460,"uid":311004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:32:54.000Z","msg":"Quora本身就是五毛集中區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:43:21.000Z","msg":"但係呢個platform比起facebook啲comment爛仔交更有用<br />\n推到多啲正確資料上Top upvote answer<br />\n之後就會多啲人見<br />\n什至會Google search嘅時候已經show埋answer"},{"pid":"d641056db3a06c0d756034a122375d430d657b15","tid":1506460,"uid":293282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0066b24350a430ec2b860b8039b06016f5936b09","tid":1506460,"uid":60208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f14b7f4e351c0b1d9b352d5ffa2e1d65162e1e45","tid":1506460,"uid":311004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:32:54.000Z","m